{"title":"重提延安","authors":["耿翔"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":8,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"重提延安"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耿翔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"许多情景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还在窑洞里。一座山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条河，不管岁月怎么歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是淳厚无比的圣土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延安，这用流水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带走困难的地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留在身边是泥土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守在身边是人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从放下枪杆的那天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就重整家园。坡地上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们不得歇息的背影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙碌得无暇回首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延安，很少提及"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些辉煌的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睁开眼睛是土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闭上眼睛是土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"质朴和诚实，是覆盖人间的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最纯粹的种子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手摸这片，有血有汗的泥土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不能轻松地离去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重提延安"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然是一身素朴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在它布满"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恩情的大地上，被歌声染绿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨日的风，今日的雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是杨家岭和枣园"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}